Package automail

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DeliveryAttachment
    The interface for Robot delivery attachments to carry different items
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Automail
    Represents the automail system, an aggregation of robots and a mail pool.
    DeliveryItem
    This is the abstract version of the delivery item, mail and food items inherits from here
    FloorManager
    Class for robot to use to ensure that nothing is delivered to a floor that food is being delivered too
    FoodAttachment
    A type of delivery attachment used for delivering food.
    FoodItem
    Represents a food item
    MailAttachment
    Represents a Mail attachment to the robot to deliver regular mail
    MailItem
    Represents a mail item
    MailPool
    addToPool is called when there are mail items newly arrived at the building to add to the MailPool or if a robot returns with some undelivered items - these are added back to the MailPool.
    Robot
    The robot delivers mail and food!
    RobotStatistics
    Keeps track of the stats of the robots.
